ZH: 我不吸香烟。
EN: I don't smoke cigarettes.
ZH: 昨天他抽了一包香烟。
EN: Yesterday he smoked a pack of cigarettes.
ZH: 这是我的最后一根香烟了。
EN: This is my last cigarette.
ZH: 我戒了香烟已经有两年了。
EN: I have quit smoking cigarettes for two years.
ZH: 我喜欢闻烟草的香味。
EN: I enjoy the smell of tobacco.
ZH: 她在早晨喜欢喝一杯咖啡和吸一根香烟。
EN: She likes to have a cup of coffee and smoke a cigarette in the mornings.
ZH: 请不要在这里吸香烟。
EN: Please do not smoke cigarettes here.
ZH: 他习惯了在工作时吸一根香烟。
EN: He is used to smoking a cigarette while working.
ZH: 吸香烟对身体有害。
EN: Smoking cigarettes is harmful to health.
ZH: 他已经戒了三个月的香烟。
EN: He has been quit for three months.
ZH: 香烟的味道常常给人一种放松的感觉。
EN: The smell of cigarettes often gives a relaxing feeling.
