EN: I have never smoked cigarettes before.
ZH: 这个城市禁止在公共场所吸香烟。
EN: Smoking cigarettes is prohibited in public places in this city.
ZH: 香烟的价格越来越高。
EN: The price of cigarettes keeps increasing.
ZH: 那个人在一口接一口地吸着烟。
EN: The person was puffing on the cigarette one after another.
ZH: 我觉得吸香烟是一种浪费金钱的习惯。
EN: I believe smoking cigarettes is a waste of money.
ZH: 我决心戒掉香烟。
